## Setup & Usage

1. Clone repo & go inside folder:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/rohit0472/TrapScan.git
cd TrapScan

Install dependency:

pip install fpdf

Run scans:

# Scan a single URL
python3 trapscan.py www.example.com

# Scan an email
python3 trapscan.py user@example.com

# Scan multiple inputs from file & export PDF
python3 trapscan.py -f input.txt --pdf

Blacklist Format

Place blacklist.txt in the project root (not inside a folder).

One domain per line. Example:

example.com
phishingsite.net
maliciousdomain.org
paypal-login-secure.com
free-gift2024.com
